cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.DS

The paper deals with video analysis and retrieval, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The use of Locality Sensitive Hashing (LSH) and fast optimal sequence alignment algorithm (FOGSAA) also suggests the involvement of information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel scheme for hashing data points based on their context, which involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) sub-category.
